40:33.369 --> 40:36.785
Essa, thank you for coming so quickly.

40:41.044 --> 40:42.443
What do you want?

40:42.445 --> 40:45.446
There is a book full of names.

40:45.448 --> 40:47.066
I'll bring you book.

40:47.069 --> 40:50.203
No, I want it destroyed.

40:50.206 --> 40:51.819
Where is?

40:51.821 --> 40:54.422
At a shrine built from red sandstone,

40:54.424 --> 40:56.123
called Maer-Nokh.

40:56.125 --> 40:58.392
You'll find it straight
south of the Ridgeline.

40:58.394 --> 41:02.863
In the Sanctum, there is
an altar, the altar of fire.

41:02.865 --> 41:06.000
Inside the altar, you'll find the book.

41:06.002 --> 41:08.302
Bring me one page as proof,

41:08.304 --> 41:10.571
burn the rest.

41:10.573 --> 41:13.441
I take one tenth now,

41:13.443 --> 41:16.143
and the rest I come get
when book is no more.

41:18.848 --> 41:20.848
If you encounter opposition...

41:20.850 --> 41:23.651
I kill anything that comes near book.

41:23.653 --> 41:25.653
That works.

41:25.655 --> 41:26.787
Huh.

